                            </item>
                            <item xml:id="a5">
                              <locus target="#120r"/>
                              <desc type="MagicText" xml:lang="am">An Amharic paryer for release from unluck with references to <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3530OldTes">Old Testament</ref>, <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS11430Apostles">Apostles</persName>, and cases in Ethiopic literaturte.</desc>
